OL,3,CHigh risk, high reward: How big is
OL,4,CBurnham's by-election gamble?
OL,6,FThe party secured just under a third
OL,7,Fof the vote, placing Makerfield among
OL,8,FReform's strongest performances
OL,9,Fnationally.
OL,11,FIn fact, the constituency recorded the
OL,12,Fsixth-highest Reform vote share in the
OL,13,Fcountry. Of the five constituencies
OL,14,Fabove it, Reform succeeded in electing
OL,15,FMPs in four.
OL,17,FAt last week's local elections, Reform
OL,18,Fswept all 11 wards in and around the
OL,19,Fconstituency, securing around half the
OL,20,Fvote across the area.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
