OL,3,CHigh risk, high reward: How big is
OL,4,CBurnham's by-election gamble?
OL,6,FNigel Farage has already made clear
OL,7,Fthat Reform would target the seat
OL,8,Faggressively in any by-election
OL,9,Fcampaign, raising the prospect of a
OL,10,Fhighly contested race.
OL,12,FLabour may also face pressure from
OL,13,Fanother direction. The Green Party,
OL,14,Fwhile viewed as an outsider, has
OL,15,Findicated it intends to mount a
OL,16,Fserious campaign.
OL,18,FThe threat is not necessarily that the
OL,19,FGreens could win, but that they could
OL,20,Ferode Labour's vote share.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
