OL,3,CHigh risk, high reward: How big is
OL,4,CBurnham's by-election gamble?
OL,6,FParty strategists will remember
OL,7,FFebruary's shock result in Gorton and
OL,8,FDenton, where the Greens overturned a
OL,9,FLabour majority of more than 13,000.
OL,10,FIf they can take votes off the Labour
OL,11,Fcandidate in a tight race, it could
OL,12,Fget interesting.
OL,14,FBurnham hopes his personal profile and
OL,15,Fpopularity across Greater Manchester
OL,16,Fcan withstand those pressures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
