OL,3,CHigh risk, high reward: How big is
OL,4,CBurnham's by-election gamble?
OL,6,FAs ITV News Political Analyst Colin
OL,7,FRallings told me today, Burnham is
OL,8,Fperhaps the only Labour figure who
OL,9,Fwould have a chance of winning this
OL,10,Fseat. But the political stakes are
OL,11,Fexceptionally high for him.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
