OL,3,CHigh risk, high reward: How big is
OL,4,CBurnham's by-election gamble?
OL,6,FDefeat would not only end Burnham's
OL,7,Ftenure as mayor of Greater Manchester
OL,8,F- he'll have to resign to contest the
OL,9,Fseat - it would also effectively end
OL,10,Fhis hopes of being prime minister.
OL,12,FVictory, however, would allow him to
OL,13,Fargue that he can succeed where others
OL,14,Fcannot: defeating Reform.
OL,16,FFor Burnham, this is high risk, high
OL,17,Freward.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
